cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SE

This paper discusses the development of a Python toolbox for inspecting fairness, accountability, and transparency in machine learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Cryptography and Security). The paper also touches on issues related to cybersecurity and software engineering, which could place it in the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) sub-categories, respectively.
